The following is the usage example.

```javascript
// Get the SVG element
const svg = document. querySelector ('svg' ) ;

// Remove and add a style class.
svgToggleClass ( svg, "my-new-class" ) ;

// Remove and add a style class with override.
svgToggleClass ( svg, "my-new-class", true )
```

